title: Frank Sinatra Love Songs [FLAC+MP3](Big Papi) 2001 Remastered
description:
Source: 2001 CD CK 61056 Volume Normalized Peak-to-Peak


Valentine's day is right around the corner so grab this and other love songs. Make your loved one a nice picnic or dinner and play some nice quiet romantic songs in the background. Be meek and mild to her in the day so she can be wild to you at night. Treat her well and she will treat you well. 

- Big Papi



By Ron 

This is an excellent collection of ballads by the young Frank Sinatra. I already own the 12 cd Columbia boxed set, but I had to get this because it includes 6 unreleased alternate takes. Columbia has done a wonderful job in thier Sinatra compilation cd's by nearly always including extra tracks like these. Even though it contains very few of his famous hits, this whole cd is fantastic.
